790
00:41:37,357 --> 00:41:39,425
<i>And they didn't believe her.</i>

791
00:41:39,459 --> 00:41:40,827
HENRIETTA: <i>They thought
the lady was crazy, right?</i>

792
00:41:40,860 --> 00:41:44,330
KITTY: <i>Mm-hmm.
So, she called 911 again,</i>

793
00:41:44,364 --> 00:41:46,499
<i>and they still
