00:46:28,814 --> 00:46:31,684
CANDYMAN (softly):
<i>Anthony...</i>

878
00:47:03,283 --> 00:47:04,951
(groans)

879
00:47:17,264 --> 00:47:19,699
- (knocks on wall)
- ANTHONY: Finley?

