horn blaring)

896
00:49:44,844 --> 00:49:46,246
(low, muffled conversations)

897
00:49:46,279 --> 00:49:47,780
MAN (muffled):
Really?

898
00:49:47,813 --> 00:49:50,217
No one's buying it,
not that I care.

899
00:49:50,250 --> 00:49:52,785
(conversation continues
